<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Using the fab four to help you kill Dwigus or Bilge is not a good idea. After reading the above post I tried it on bosuns and tidal lords. Out of 15 I dragged to the heros I was unable to ever get the exp or loot from a single one. Once the fab four attacks it is gone and I bet that is true for Bilge also.</font></td></tr></table>
